article_title: Check out what David Axelrod finds 'seductive' – twitchy.com
article_text:
Seductive? You make the mockery so easy, Axe.

Whatever you think of Rep. Fred Upton’s Obamacare bill, this right here is funny:

Dude. You're thinking of Kate Upton. MT @davidaxelrod Given current firestorm over coverage drops, Upton bill is seductive. — jon gabriel (@exjon) November 14, 2013

He has company:
